ocs/design/`)\n38: \n39: | File | Status | Description |\n40: |------|--------|-------------|\n41: | `coding-standards.md` | ✅ **Created** | Go/Python 代码规范、测试标准 |\n42: | `naming-conventions.md` | ✅ **Created** | CRD、API Group、环境变量命名 |\n43: | `error-handling.md` | ✅ **Created** | 错误类型、处理模式、HTTP 响应 |\n44: \n45: ### Documentation Guide (`docs/`)\n46: \n47: | File | Status | Description |\n48: |------|--------|-------------|\n49: | `README.md` | ✅ **Created** | 文档结构说明、读者指南、贡献指南 |\n50: \n51: ### Docusaurus Integration\n52: \n53: | File | Status | Description |\n54: |------|--------|-------------|\n55: | `sidebars.ts` | ✅ **Updated** | 添加 Architecture、API Reference、Design Specifications 导航 |\n56: \n57: ## Acceptance Criteria Verification\n58: \n59: ### Architecture Documentation ✅\n60: \n61: - [x] `docs/architecture/` — Directory exists\n62: - [x] `docs/architecture/overview.md` — Contains system vision and layered architecture diagram\n63: - [x] `docs/architecture/overview.md` — Contains component table with responsibilities\n64: - [x] `docs/architecture/overview.md` — Documents key design decisions\n65: - [x] `docs/architecture/components.md` — Documents Router with interface\n66: - [x] `docs/architecture/components.md` — Documents Workload Manager with CRD watch\n67: - [x] `docs/architecture/components.md` — Documents Store with Redis integration\n68: - [x] `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` — Documents session creation flow\n69: - [x] `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` — Documents request routing flow\n70: - [x] `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` — Documents session expiration flow\n71: - [x] `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` — Documents sandbox lifecycle states\n72: - [x] `docs/architecture/deployment.md` — Documents Kind development deployment\n73: - [x] `docs/architecture/deployment.md` — Documents multi-cluster production deployment\n74: - [x] `docs/architecture/deployment.md` — Contains resource configuration table\n75: - [x] `docs/architecture/security.md` — Contains security boundary diagram\n76: - [x] `docs/architecture/security.md` — Documents authentication mechanisms\n77: - [x] `docs/architecture/security.md` — Documents sandbox security measures\n78: \n79: ### API Documentation ✅\n80: \n81: - [x] `docs/api/` — Directory exists\n82: - [x] `docs/api/README.md` — API documentation index exists\n83: - [x] `docs/api/router.md` — Documents POST/GET/DELETE /api/v1/sessions endpoints\n84: - [x] `docs/api/router.md` — Contains JSON request/response examples\n85: - [x] `docs/api/router.md` — Contains Python SDK usage example\n86: - [x] `docs/api/workload-manager.md` — Documents workload CRUD and scale endpoints\n87: - [x] `docs/api/workload-manager.md` — Contains JSON request/response examples\n88: - [x] `docs/api/store.md` — Documents Store interface with Set/Get/Delete/Exists/Watch\n89: - [x] `docs/api/store.md` — Documents Event struct and EventType constants\n90: - [x] `docs/api/store.md` — Contains Go usage example\n91: - [x] `docs/api/sandbox-manager.md` — Documents SandboxManager interface\n92: - [x] `docs/api/sandbox-manager.md` — Documents WarmPoolManager interface\n93: - [x] `docs/api/sandbox-manager.md` — Contains Go usage example\n94: - [x] `docs/api/picod.md` — Documents PicoD interface with Run/Start/RunWithStreaming\n95: - [x] `docs/api/picod.md` — Documents Command and CommandResult structs\n96: - [x] `docs/api/picod.md` — Contains Go usage example\n97: - [x] `docs/api/picod.md` — Documents POST /execute and GET /health HTTP endpoints\n98: \n99: ### Design Specifications ✅\n100: \n101: - [x] `docs/design/` — Directory exists\n102: - [x] `docs/design/coding-standards.md` — Documents Go formatting standards\n103: - [x] `docs/design/coding-standards.md` — Documents naming standards\n104: - [x] `docs/design/coding-standards.md` — Documents error handling standards\n105: - [x] `docs/design/coding-standards.md` — Documents testing standards\n106: - [x] `docs/design/naming-conventions.md` — Documents CRD naming conventions\n