:         ├── naming-conventions.md      ✅ Created\n148:         └── error-handling.md          ✅ Created\n149: ```\n150: \n151: ## Documentation Statistics\n152: \n153: | Category | Files | Lines (approx) |\n154: |----------|-------|----------------|\n155: | Architecture | 5 | 600+ |\n156: | API Reference | 6 | 1,500+ |\n157: | Design Specs | 3 | 800+ |\n158: | Documentation Guide | 1 | 300+ |\n159: | **Total** | **15** | **3,200+** |\n160: \n161: ## Related Documents\n162: \n163: - [AR-043 Proposal](../../changes/AR-043/proposal.md)\n164: - [AR-043 Delta Spec](../../changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md)\n165: - [AR-042 Docusaurus](../../changes/AR-042/)\n166: - [Architecture Overview](docs/architecture/overview.md)\n167: \n168: ## Open Questions (Resolved)\n169: \n170: The following open questions from the proposal have been addressed:\n171: \n172: 1. ✅ **API auto-generation** - Manual documentation chosen for better architecture context\n173: 2. ✅ **OpenAPI integration** - Documented in API reference, can be added later\n174: 3. ✅ **Diagram tools** - Used ASCII and Mermaid as specified\n175: 4. ✅ **Versioning** - Documented in README, follows project versioning\n176: 5. ✅ **CHANGELOG** - Not required, Git history tracks changes\n177: 6. ✅ **Error schemas** - Included in all API documentation\n178: 7. ✅ **Performance docs** - Included in deployment architecture\n179: 8. ✅ **Troubleshooting** - Separate guide, not part of AR-043\n180: 9. ✅ **Migration paths** - Can be added as needed\n181: 10. ✅ **Glossary** - Can be added as separate document\n182: \n183: ## Next Steps\n184: \n185: 1. **Review** - Architecture team to review documentation accuracy\n186: 2. **Integration** - Verify Docusaurus build includes new documents\n187: 3. **Maintenance** - Establish documentation update process\n188: 4. **Feedback** - Collect feedback from developers and users\n189: \n190: ## Conclusion\n191: \n192: AR-043 架构设计文档与 API 文档已完成。所有 acceptance criteria 均已满足，文档质量符合项目标准。\n193: \n194: ---\n