{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775895529728,"sessionID":"ses_284611580ffeIf38TurH3phN6H","part":{"id":"prt_d7b9f3cbf001bhiVWzBizb45lZ","messageID":"msg_d7b9f206f001v95dRYW73lLi19","sessionID":"ses_284611580ffeIf38TurH3phN6H","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_d53b3697a0104fc7ae8cda48","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md","limit":150},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Specification — AR-043: 架构设计文档与 API 文档\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: **Module:** `docs`  \n6: **Language:** Markdown  \n7: **Size:** M  \n8: **Type:** Architecture design and API documentation for agentcube project\n9: \n10: **Base Specs:** (No directly matching specs)\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## Requirements & Scenarios\n15: \n16: ### REQ-043.1: Architecture Documentation Structure\n17: \n18: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide an `docs/architecture/` directory with architecture design documentation.\n19: \n20: #### Scenario: Architecture directory exists\n21: - **GIVEN** the agentcube repository root\n22: - **WHEN** the documentation structure is inspected\n23: - **THEN** `docs/architecture/` directory SHALL exist\n24: \n25: #### Scenario: Architecture overview document\n26: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/` directory exists\n27: - **WHEN** documentation content is inspected\n28: - **THEN** `docs/architecture/overview.md` SHALL provide system architecture overview\n29: \n30: #### Scenario: Architecture overview contains system vision\n31: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/overview.md` exists\n32: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n33: - **THEN** it SHALL describe AgentCube's vision as Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform\n34: \n35: #### Scenario: Architecture overview contains layered diagram\n36: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/overview.md` exists\n37: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n38: - **THEN** it SHALL include ASCII or Mermaid diagram showing Client Layer, API Gateway, Session Routing, Workload Manager, Sandbox Orchestration, and State Storage\n39: \n40: #### Scenario: Architecture overview contains component table\n41: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/overview.md` exists\n42: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n43: - **THEN** it SHALL include table listing Router, Workload Manager, Sandbox Manager, Store, and PicoD with their responsibilities and tech stack\n44: \n45: #### Scenario: Architecture overview contains design decisions\n46: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/overview.md` exists\n47: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n48: - **THEN** it SHALL document key design decisions: Kubernetes-native, session affinity, warm pool optimization, and isolated execution\n49: \n50: #### Scenario: Core components design document\n51: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/` directory exists\n52: - **WHEN** documentation content is inspected\n53: - **THEN** `docs/architecture/components.md` SHALL provide detailed component designs\n54: \n55: #### Scenario: Router component documentation\n56: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/components.md` exists\n57: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n58: - **THEN** it SHALL document Router's responsibilities, architecture diagram, and key interfaces\n59: \n60: #### Scenario: Workload Manager component documentation\n61: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/components.md` exists\n62: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n63: - **THEN** it SHALL document Workload Manager's responsibilities, architecture diagram, and CRD watch mechanism\n64: \n65: #### Scenario: Store component documentation\n66: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/components.md` exists\n67: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n68: - **THEN** it SHALL document Store's responsibilities, Redis/Valkey integration, and architecture\n69: \n70: #### Scenario: Data flow design document\n71: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/` directory exists\n72: - **WHEN** documentation content is inspected\n73: - **THEN** `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` SHALL describe data flow and request processing\n74: \n75: #### Scenario: Session creation flow\n76: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` exists\n77: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n78: - **THEN** it SHALL document the session creation flow: Client → Router → Store → Workload Manager → Sandbox Pod\n79: \n80: #### Scenario: Request routing flow\n81: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` exists\n82: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n83: - **THEN** it SHALL document the request routing flow: Client → Router → Store → Backend URL lookup → Agent Pod\n84: \n85: #### Scenario: Session expiration flow\n86: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` exists\n87: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n88: - **THEN** it SHALL document the session expiration flow: TTL expires → Redis key deleted → Keyspace notification → Workload Manager deletes sandbox\n89: \n90: #### Scenario: Sandbox lifecycle states\n91: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/data-flow.md` exists\n92: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n93: - **THEN** it SHALL document sandbox lifecycle states: Pending → Creating → Running → Idle → Terminating → Terminated\n94: \n95: #### Scenario: Deployment architecture document\n96: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/` directory exists\n97: - **WHEN** documentation content is inspected\n98: - **THEN** `docs/architecture/deployment.md` SHALL describe deployment architectures\n99: \n100: #### Scenario: Development environment deployment\n101: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/deployment.md` exists\n102: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n103: - **THEN** it SHALL document Kind cluster deployment with agentcube-system namespace\n104: \n105: #### Scenario: Production environment deployment\n106: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/deployment.md` exists\n107: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n108: - **THEN** it SHALL document multi-cluster production deployment with load balancer\n109: \n110: #### Scenario: Resource configuration table\n111: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/deployment.md` exists\n112: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n113: - **THEN** it SHALL include resource configuration table with CPU/Memory requests and limits for Router, Workload Manager, Redis, and Sandbox Pod\n114: \n115: #### Scenario: Security architecture document\n116: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/` directory exists\n117: - **WHEN** documentation content is inspected\n118: - **THEN** `docs/architecture/security.md` SHALL describe security architecture\n119: \n120: #### Scenario: Security boundary diagram\n121: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/security.md` exists\n122: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n123: - **THEN** it SHALL include security boundary diagram showing External Network, API Gateway, Internal Network, and Sandbox Pod\n124: \n125: #### Scenario: Authentication and authorization\n126: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/security.md` exists\n127: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n128: - **THEN** it SHALL document authentication mechanisms: JWT Token, mTLS, RSA Key Pair for PicoD, and Kubernetes RBAC\n129: \n130: #### Scenario: Sandbox security measures\n131: - **GIVEN** `docs/architecture/security.md` exists\n132: - **WHEN** content is evaluated\n133: - **THEN** it SHALL document sandbox security: non-root user, read-only root FS, dropped capabilities, syscall restrictions, namespace isolation, and resource quotas\n134: \n135: ---\n136: \n137: ### REQ-043.2: API Documentation Structure\n138: \n139: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide a `docs/api/` directory with API documentation for all core components.\n140: \n141: #### Scenario: API directory exists\n142: - **GIVEN** the agentcube repository root\n143: - **WHEN** the documentation structure is inspected\n144: - **THEN** `docs/api/` directory SHALL exist\n145: \n146: #### Scenario: API README index\n147: - **GIVEN** `docs/api/` directory exists\n148: - **WHEN** documentation content is inspected\n149: - **THEN** `docs/api/README.md` SHALL provide API documentation index\n150: \n\n(Showing lines 1-150 of 639. Use offset=151 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Specification — AR-043: 架构设计文档与 API 文档\n\n## Overview\n\n**Module:** `docs`  \n**Language:** Markdown  \n**Size:** M  \n**Type:** Architecture design and API documentation for agentcube project\n\n**Base Specs:** (No directly matching specs)\n\n---\n\n## Requirements & Scenarios\n\n### REQ-043.1: Architecture Documentation Structure\n\n**Requirement:** The system SHALL provide an `docs/architecture/` directory with architecture design documentation.\n\n#### Scenario: Architecture directory exists","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-043/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775895529701,"end":1775895529727}}}}
