namespace\": \"default\",\n68:   \"phase\": \"Pending\",\n69:   \"podName\": \"\",\n70:   \"endpoints\": [],\n71:   \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-11T15:30:00Z\"\n72: }\n73: ```\n74: \n75: **Status Codes:**\n76: \n77: - `201 Created` - Sandbox created successfully\n78: - `400 Bad Request` - Invalid input\n79: - `409 Conflict` - Sandbox already exists\n80: \n81: #### Get Sandbox\n82: \n83: Retrieves sandbox information.\n84: \n85: **Endpoint:**\n86: \n87: ```http\n88: GET /sandboxes/{sandboxId}\n89: ```\n90: \n91: **Response:**\n92: \n93: ```json\n94: {\n95:   \"sandboxId\": \"sandbox-abc\",\n96:   \"name\": \"sandbox-abc\",\n97:   \"namespace\": \"default\",\n98:   \"phase\": \"Running\",\n99:   \"podName\": \"sandbox-abc-pod-xyz\",\n100:   \"podIP\": \"10.244.0.5\",\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 447. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\nid: workload-manager-api\ntitle: Workload Manager API\nslug: /api-reference/workload-manager\nsidebar_label: Workload Manager API\n---\n\n# Workload Manager API\n\nThe Workload Manager API provides sandbox lifecycle management and resource orchestration.\n\n## Base URL\n\n```\nhttp://workload-manager:8081/api/v1\n```\n\n## Authentication\n\nService-to-service communication requires authentication:","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/docs/docs/api/workload-manager.md","time":{"start":1775895571940,"end":1775895571958}}}}
